translate spanish marip2_967f58d3:

    # fr "Sure, it's fine."
    fr "Claro, no pasa nada."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:14
translate spanish marip2_5d6bc487:

    # fr "I mean, it's not something I want to do the rest of my life."
    fr "Quiero decir, no es algo que quiera hacer el resto de mi vida."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:15
translate spanish marip2_16d89d66:

    # fr "I don't want to be there at sixty-years-old like Connie and Jackson, but I don't mind doing it to pay the bills."
    fr "No quiero estar ahí a los sesenta años como Connie y Jackson, pero no me importa hacerlo para pagar las facturas."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:16
translate spanish marip2_7f8bd6cb:

    # fr "It's expensive to keep a farm running. I sell some of the stuff I grow, but not enough to pay for everything."
    fr "Mantener una granja en marcha es caro. Vendo algunas de las cosas que cultivo, pero no lo suficiente para pagarlo todo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:17
translate spanish marip2_fcb7049e:

    # fr "Jackson is nice too. He's a great boss."
    fr "Jackson también es majo. Es un jefe estupendo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:22
translate spanish marip2_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mari_really.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_really.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:23
translate spanish marip2_82a3c0a4:

    # fr "Really? You think so?"
    fr "¿En serio? ¿Tú crees?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:24
translate spanish marip2_55026cfb:

    # fr "Most of the people I talk to think he's a sleaze-ball."
    fr "La mayoría de la gente con la que hablo piensa que es un canalla."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:25
translate spanish marip2_9be30a68:

    # fr "He kind of has that thing going on with him, especially since he only hires young pretty girls."
    fr "Tiene ese aire, sobre todo porque solo contrata a chicas jóvenes y guapas."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:26
translate spanish marip2_e0167be8:

    # fr "And Connie, who I've never got a straight answer out of as to how she got that job."
    fr "Y Connie, de quien nunca he conseguido una respuesta clara sobre cómo consiguió ese trabajo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:28
translate spanish marip2_d1119f2e:

    # fr "Anyways, a lot of people think that he takes advantage of young girls, but it's kind of the opposite actually."
    fr "En fin, mucha gente piensa que se aprovecha de las chicas jóvenes, pero en realidad es más bien al revés."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:31
translate spanish marip2_9d3a782e:

    # fr "I'm not surprised. Most people think he's like that."
    fr "No me sorprende. La mayoría de la gente piensa que es así."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:32
translate spanish marip2_6f723387:

    # pc "What's with him only hiring young pretty girls? Seems kind of weird."
    pc "¿Por qué solo contrata a chicas jóvenes y guapas? Me parece un poco raro."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:33
translate spanish marip2_67c4a58d:

    # fr "Yeah, a lot of people think he takes advantage of us, but it's kind of the opposite actually."
    fr "Sí, mucha gente piensa que se aprovecha de nosotras, pero en realidad es más bien al revés."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:35
translate spanish marip2_714a6ca0:

    # fr "He lost his daughter when she was a little younger than me. Cancer."
    fr "Perdió a su hija cuando era un poco más joven que yo. De cáncer."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:36
translate spanish marip2_0b313e81:

    # fr "His wife had died during child birth and his daughter was everything to him."
    fr "Su mujer había muerto durante el parto y su hija lo era todo para él."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:38
translate spanish marip2_2b0d347b:

    # fr "He hires young pretty girls because they remind him of his daughter. He overpays too - I think I actually take home more every week than even he does."
    fr "Contrata a chicas jóvenes y guapas porque le recuerdan a su hija. Además, nos paga de más; creo que, de hecho, me llevo a casa cada semana más dinero que él mismo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:39
translate spanish marip2_7604f613:

    # fr "But he likes doing it. He likes supporting young girls, seeing them grow up into strong women."
    fr "Pero le gusta hacerlo. Le gusta apoyar a las chicas jóvenes, verlas crecer y convertirse en mujeres fuertes."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:40
translate spanish marip2_802331e3:

    # fr "Because he never got a chance to see his own girl grow up."
    fr "Porque nunca tuvo la oportunidad de ver crecer a su propia hija."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:41
translate spanish marip2_0da0091b:

    # pc "Wow that's sad. I feel so bad for him."
    pc "Vaya, qué triste. Lo siento mucho por él."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:42
translate spanish marip2_976158ed:

    # fr "Yeah, me too. But I think he's in a good place now."
    fr "Sí, yo también. Pero creo que ahora está bien."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:43
translate spanish marip2_46f3f9a0:

    # pc "What about the customers? I bet you deal with a lot of guys hitting on you all the time."
    pc "¿Y los clientes? Apuesto a que tienes que lidiar con un montón de tíos que intentan ligar contigo todo el tiempo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:45
translate spanish marip2_4647b21b:

    # fr "Oh you wouldn't believe how many."
    fr "Oh, no te imaginas cuántos."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:46
translate spanish marip2_2f392771:

    # fr "I'm always having guys call me sweetheart or pinch my butt."
    fr "Siempre hay tíos que me llaman «cariño» o me pellizcan el culo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:51
translate spanish marip2_e35218de:

    # fr "Nah, it's just harmless flirting."
    fr "No, solo es coqueteo inofensivo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:52
translate spanish marip2_180e4570:

    # fr "I usually get a few extra bucks out of it."
    fr "Normalmente consigo unos cuantos dólares extra gracias a eso."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:53
translate spanish marip2_d6575bd6:

    # fr "And I remember the guys who don't tip. I'm never as friendly to them a second time."
    fr "Y me acuerdo de los que no dejan propina. Nunca vuelvo a ser tan amable con ellos."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:56
translate spanish marip2_6b5565d7:

    # fr "Why not? It's just harmless flirting."
    fr "¿Por qué no? Solo es un coqueteo inofensivo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:57
translate spanish marip2_33bad6b6:

    # pc "They're harassing you though."
    pc "Pero te están acosando."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:59
translate spanish marip2_244ae1b8:

    # fr "Nah, it's not harassment."
    fr "No, no es acoso."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:60
translate spanish marip2_9d05e9f7:

    # fr "I flirt just as much as they do."
    fr "Yo coqueteo tanto como ellos."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:61
translate spanish marip2_d6575bd6_1:

    # fr "And I remember the guys who don't tip. I'm never as friendly to them a second time."
    fr "Y me acuerdo de los chicos que no dejan propina. La segunda vez nunca soy tan amable con ellos."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:65
translate spanish marip2_095c76b9:

    # fr "Yeah I am. It's just harmless flirting though."
    fr "Sí, lo soy. Pero solo es un coqueteo inofensivo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:66
translate spanish marip2_63def094:

    # fr "If I make a few extra bucks by wiggling my butt a bit, what's the harm?"
    fr "Si gano unos cuantos dólares extra meneando un poco el trasero, ¿qué hay de malo?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:67
translate spanish marip2_d6575bd6_2:

    # fr "And I remember the guys who don't tip. I'm never as friendly to them a second time."
    fr "Y me acuerdo de los chicos que no dejan propina. La segunda vez nunca soy tan amable con ellos."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:69
translate spanish marip2_4bdb229b:

    # fr "Does that bother you?"
    fr "¿Te molesta eso?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:73
translate spanish marip2_259facae:

    # fr "That's okay. It's normal to be a little jealous."
    fr "No pasa nada. Es normal estar un poco celoso."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:74
translate spanish marip2_71f1f7d8:

    # fr "Just know that I'll never lie to you."
    fr "Solo quiero que sepas que nunca te mentiré."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:75
translate spanish marip2_29314cd7:

    # fr "If this dating thing turns into something serious, I'll never cheat on you."
    fr "Si esto de salir juntos se convierte en algo serio, nunca te seré infiel."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:76
translate spanish marip2_910956c8:

    # fr "It's just flirting, and I'll never flirt with another guy in front of you. I'll never make you feel bad."
    fr "Solo es coquetear, y nunca coquetearé con otro chico delante de ti. Nunca te haré sentir mal."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:78
translate spanish marip2_faa0aa36:

    # fr "And out of all the guys that I flirt with, you're the only one I'm going on a date with."
    fr "Y de todos los chicos con los que coqueteo, tú eres el único con el que voy a salir."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:79
translate spanish marip2_139aa3e2:

    # fr "Just you."
    fr "Solo tú."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:82
translate spanish marip2_5b8c91bf:

    # fr "That's good."
    fr "Eso está bien."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:83
translate spanish marip2_6f646561:

    # fr "Because out of all the guys that I flirt with, you're the only one I'm going on a date with."
    fr "Porque de todos los chicos con los que coqueteo, tú eres el único con el que voy a salir."

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip2.rpy:84
translate spanish marip2_b77c1c3d:

    # fr "So no reason to be jealous."
    fr "Así que no hay motivo para estar celoso."

